#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:171
msgid "Getting a JWT token for API testing"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:173
msgid ""
"To test API endpoints directly (without the browser), obtain a token via "
"curl. First retrieve the client secret from Keycloak Admin:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:175
msgid "Open `http://localhost:8080`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:176
msgid "Login: `admin` / `admin` → select realm **ronl**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:177
msgid "Navigate to **Clients → ronl-business-api → Credentials**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:178
msgid "Copy the **Client secret**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:180
msgid "Then request a token:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:182
msgid ""
"TOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8080/realms/ronl/protocol/openid-"
"connect/token \\\n"
"  -H \"Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\" \\\n"
"  -d \"client_id=ronl-business-api\" \\\n"
"  -d \"client_secret=<YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET>\" \\\n"
"  -d \"username=test-citizen-utrecht\" \\\n"
"  -d \"password=test123\" \\\n"
"  -d \"grant_type=password\" \\\n"
"  | jq -r '.access_token')\n"
"\n"
"echo \"Token: $TOKEN\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:195
msgid "Call a protected endpoint with the token:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:197
msgid ""
"curl -X POST http://localhost:3002/v1/process/zorgtoeslag/start \\\n"
"  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n"
"  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n"
"  -d '{\n"
"    \"variables\": {\n"
"      \"ingezeteneVanNederland\": true,\n"
"      \"18JaarOfOuder\": true,\n"
"      \"zorgverzekeringInNederland\": true,\n"
"      \"inkomenEnVermogen\": 24000\n"
"    }\n"
"  }' | jq"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:213
msgid "Database access"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:215
msgid "Inspect the audit log database while the Docker services are running:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:217
msgid ""
"docker exec -it ronl-postgres psql -U postgres\n"
"\n"
"# Switch to audit database\n"
"\\c audit_logs\n"
"\n"
"# View recent audit entries\n"
"SELECT * FROM audit_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;\n"
"\n"
"# View tenants\n"
"SELECT * FROM tenants;\n"
"\n"
"# Exit\n"
"\\q"
msgstr ""

